# TalentLens AI — Environment Configuration

# Google Gemini API Key
# Required for AI-based Resume parsing, Skill DNA graph fusion, and match explanations.
# Get a free key from Google AI Studio: https://aistudio.google.com/
GEMINI_API_KEY=

# GitHub Personal Access Token
# Optional, but highly recommended. Without this, GitHub limits the server to 60 requests/hour.
# With a token, the server gets 5,000 requests/hour.
# Create a token here: https://github.com/settings/tokens (No scopes are needed for reading public repos)
GITHUB_TOKEN=
